{"blocks":[{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"# Risk Analysis for AAPL (Refreshed)\n","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"markdown"}},"type":"codeTool"},{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"This notebook analyzes the strategic risk evolution for **AAPL** based on reported SEC categories.\n","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"markdown"}},"type":"codeTool"},{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"{\n  const risks = graph.nodes({category: 'Risk'}).map(n => ({\n    label: n.properties.label,\n    year: n.properties.year,\n    section: n.properties.section,\n    description: n.properties.description\n  })).filter(r => r.year).sort((a,b) => a.year - b.year);\n  \n  return risks;\n}","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"javascript2","dname":"summary-data","hide":false}},"type":"codeTool"},{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"## Risk Distribution Timeline\n","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"markdown"}},"type":"codeTool"},{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"Interactive plot tracking risk reports over time.\n","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"markdown"}},"type":"codeTool"},{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"{\n  const risks = graph.nodes({category: 'Risk'}).map(n => ({\n    label: n.properties.label,\n    date: new Date(n.properties.year, 0, 1),\n    section: n.properties.section || \"Uncategorized\"\n  })).filter(d => !isNaN(d.date)).sort((a,b) => a.date - b.date);\n\n  return Plot.plot({\n    height: 400,\n    marginLeft: 100,\n    grid: true,\n    x: {label: \"Year\", tickFormat: \"d\"},\n    y: {label: \"Section\"},\n    color: {legend: true},\n    marks: [\n      Plot.dot(risks, {x: \"date\", y: \"section\", stroke: \"section\", r: 5, tip: true}),\n      Plot.text(risks, {x: \"date\", y: \"section\", text: \"label\", dy: -12, fontSize: 8, maxWidth: 100})\n    ]\n  });\n}","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"javascript2","dname":"timeline-plot","hide":false}},"type":"codeTool"},{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"## Trend Analysis Summary\n","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"markdown"}},"type":"codeTool"},{"data":{"codeData":{"value":"{\n  const risks = graph.nodes({category: 'Risk'}).map(n => n.properties);\n  const years = [...new Set(risks.map(r => r.year))].sort();\n  \n  const aiKeywords = /AI|Intelligence|Machine Learning/i;\n  const regKeywords = /Regulation|Antitrust|Legal|Government|Tax/i;\n  \n  const aiTrend = risks.filter(r => aiKeywords.test(r.label + r.description));\n  const regTrend = risks.filter(r => regKeywords.test(r.label + r.description));\n\n  return md`\n### High-Level Trends for AAPL:\n- **Timeline Range:** ${years[0]} to ${years[years.length-1]}\n- **Regulatory Pressure:** Identified **${regTrend.length}** risks associated with legal and regulatory challenges.\n- **Technology Pivot:** Identified **${aiTrend.length}** risks specifically mentioning Artificial Intelligence or ML.\n  `;\n}","pinCode":false,"codeMode":"javascript2","dname":"trend-logic","hide":false}},"type":"codeTool"}],"version":"2.19.1"}